    <name>Strategies for Adding Social Presence: Help learners create a profile​</name>
    <intro></intro>
    <introformat>1</introformat>
    <content>&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{27d76d9e-c198-4ad5-8aa9-83c9be4d8a30}{213}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.14999,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Encourage adult learners to set up their profile on the platform used to deliver the content, with&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;the option to upload a photo or video&amp;nbsp;and provide personal information they feel comfortable&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;sharing (for example, sharing where they live might be helpful for finding study partners who live&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;nearby).&amp;nbsp; You can model this as the instructor by creating your own introduction that shares your&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;passion for the subject and other personal details that may help learners relate to you on a more&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;personal level.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{27d76d9e-c198-4ad5-8aa9-83c9be4d8a30}{213}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.14999,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/divider%20wave.png" alt="" width="1920" height="195" role="presentation" class="img-responsive atto_image_button_text-bottom"&gt;​&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{27d76d9e-c198-4ad5-8aa9-83c9be4d8a30}{216}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.14999,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;​&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{27d76d9e-c198-4ad5-8aa9-83c9be4d8a30}{219}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.14999,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;​&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
